skipiste.importer.kml

Class SkiMapHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • skipiste.importer.kml.KMLHandler
        • skipiste.importer.kml.SkiMapHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class SkiMapHandler
extends KMLHandler
    Parses KML from PlanDePistes.nl. This produces a List>. Each entry in the List being a LinkedList of the nodes that make up a single ski piste in our data.
